Introduction
Application to communicate with firewall via grpc, and do HW offload on Nvidia
BlueField DPU

Usage
1. Compile DPDK and daemon
# cd firewall_offload
# . build.sh

2. Setup hugepages
3. Make sure to create 1 VF for each PF on x86 side
4. Run app
# cd firewall_offload/daemon
# ./build/firewall_offload -n 1 -w 0000:03:00.0,representor=[0] -w 0000:03:00.1,representor=[0]  -- -i
